{"tid":1486983,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"[靚到癲] 維園超靚抗爭者記者figure照瘋傳 模型達人花3個月精製","createTime":"2019-08-19T05:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T11:50:06.000Z","uid":36592,"like":53,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc120689c7e03f267dfd6ad8a04d62aa200ac37","tid":1486983,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190818/large/1566133879_a389.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190818%2Flarge%2F1566133879_a389.png&h=bf16fd23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190818/large/1566133887_f30d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190818%2Flarge%2F1566133887_f30d.jpg&h=32391cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190818/large/1566133887_225b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190818%2Flarge%2F1566133887_225b.png&h=e4f99db9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人8.18在維園外展示4個「逆權運動」參與者的模型，當中包括拿著自製「盾牌」、淋熄催淚彈的前線抗爭者，以及手執相機的攝影記者等，吸引大批集會者和途人拍照打卡，在網上廣傳。製作者之一的Cat接受《蘋果》訪問時表示，身為模型製作愛好者，冀用他們的「語言」支持這場運動，並以此鼓勵其他「玩具宅男」也可一同走出來，參與集會、遊行等。<br />\n<br />\n他透露，自6月初「反送中」運動開始，與數名朋友著手以此題材製作模型，並決定將它們帶至8.18集會中展示。他續說，由構思到完成需約3個月時間，並花費約1,000元，用來購置合適零件及加工等。他指模型主要描繪前線抗爭者，但其中一個模型描繪攝影記者，「記者都好辛苦，所以想加插入嚟」。被問到未來會否繼續把他們製作模型帶至其他集會，他指，希望可繼續展示，惟視乎「危險」情況，計畫再製作更多同類模型。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190818/59946727/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F59946727%2F&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=18aec4fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190818%2F59946727%2F&h=0cf682d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190818/59946727/</a>"},{"pid":"501406a76ad0e0e813fe36da24efb21c3b3bfdb2","tid":1486983,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:19:56.000Z","msg":"想要大波madam<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d8daedf29ccd06ce3cdf45d46937181548b031b","tid":1486983,"uid":54415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:20:51.000Z","msg":"最後有無收返呀？好靚"},{"pid":"3eedd635a054f79ee9f7f30e05d70014b314ccb7","tid":1486983,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:22:48.000Z","msg":"好靚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d729337a00e26e765702d9b13f90e13f5b8dac","tid":1486983,"uid":45373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:22:52.000Z","msg":"1000 蚊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平過買毒撚figure"},{"pid":"c3d1578ca250961846ee01a2ec5142d8c413c9b8","tid":1486983,"uid":125680,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:26:50.000Z","msg":"個記者係鬼<br />\n用警察防毒面具"},{"pid":"ce38a6f6fa8b02cf38268c9646cbe0bf3b02b1c9","tid":1486983,"uid":68664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開頭睇相唔知係figure，仲諗緊做乜擺pose影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db3a4e14dbd83b11d86ddc06c07a491f5bf74c9","tid":1486983,"uid":115715,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"3個月? 即係未開波就開始整?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93793ef6cbd3f4db03fabc15cffad148b54522bf","tid":1486983,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"3個月?"},{"pid":"1ece3ac8c0a217babef3ebf4bca7ccf44cc4f368","tid":1486983,"uid":7854,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/q_70,c_zoom,w_640/images/20181004/7344eea0d88b4b3daa46fa697c3848f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fq_70%2Cc_zoom%2Cw_640%2Fimages%2F20181004%2F7344eea0d88b4b3daa46fa697c3848f6.jpg&h=4a1f00b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18f65831f652267eb75d0e0383bd9373fe9fc4d0","tid":1486983,"uid":27670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ecpuXvi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FecpuXvi.png&h=de855324&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a09eaaa07becd2c7899d59a94a35e7f23be8c36","tid":1486983,"uid":61976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"數學大師？？"},{"pid":"aee6d7d4ab7226d51abad5c4bc7998b4ecbbafc8","tid":1486983,"uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"5月開始整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"49d6c08aa244e21122a53d4b95f98140dead5f50","tid":1486983,"uid":45498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190819/20751608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190819%2F20751608&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSsmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=f9c18b43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190819%2F20751608&h=99b6a1c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190819/20751608</a><br />\n<br />\n宅男搜集部件 製示威模型<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190819/large/1566144166_55a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190819%2Flarge%2F1566144166_55a2.jpg&h=8c43d467&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宅男製作了一套示威者的模型，除了頭盔和衣物，還有木盾牌、水馬及用棉花製的催淚煙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨午的銅鑼灣，忽然下起大雨，且連綿下了數小時，可是雨中的人潮從未散開。下雨那刻，記者正在訪問製作示威者模型的一群集會人士，他們被雨水淋得全身濕透，但仍然笑說：「催淚彈也不怕，幾滴雨怕甚麼？」後來，人群突然有幾個坐輪椅的示威者過路，人們紛紛讓路和替他們撐傘，顧不得自己會被淋濕。大風大雨裏，香港人用手中一把傘，扶持彼此。<br />\n<br />\n記者：趙曉彤<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警西環屯重兵 見黑衣即查<br />\n<br />\n維園外，有不少人蹲在地下，對着一套迷你的示威者模型拍照。這套模型，是戴口罩、眼罩、頭盔、穿着「香港」黑恤衫的示威者，也有記者，還有水馬、鐵馬、垃圾桶、以及用棉花製作的催淚煙等，仿真度甚高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喚起玩具界關心<br />\n<br />\n製作者之一林先生和陳先生皆表示，他們平日給人的印象可能是玩玩具的宅男，而其實在玩具界一直是少有談論政治的，但他和朋友因為反送中運動及對政府的不滿，就在兩、三個月前開始，決定製作一套相關的玩具，帶到街上拍照，希望可以喚起玩具界對反送中運動的關心，同時也讓其他人明白，即使是玩玩具的宅男也好，其實他們留在家裏亦會接收到不同的資訊，而同時，宅男也是可以上街發聲。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生表示，由於這套模型的主題敏感，所以現成的器材不會在同一間玩具店買到，購買散件的難度甚高，但既然他們很想製作出這套玩具，就逐間逐間玩具店去買一比六的頭盔、鐵馬、垃圾桶等等，但最後所有材料其實都可以在香港的模型舖買到，就連示威者身上所穿的迷你「香港」恤衫，也是購買得來的。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生說：「慢慢找是一定找到的，因為上街示威者穿在身上也不是很特別的裝備，都是普通工程帽、手包保鮮紙等等。」但在搜集零件的同時，他卻發現平日很易在玩具店購得的3M口罩（在替模型噴油漆時需要用），竟然有很多玩具店也買不到。<br />\n<br />\n6月9日有一百萬人上街，政府卻不回應，林先生和朋友便打算製作這個主題的模型。終於在幾天前，模型大功告成，但直至昨日的維園合法集會，他們才敢把模型放在街上拍照。令他們驚喜的是，很多香港人也停下來替模型拍照，並跟他們說加油，令他們更感受到，大家其實是很愛香港的。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：醫護撐爆眼女 聲討高永文<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥政府無視市民<br />\n<br />\n兩位宅男只曾參與過6.9一百萬人及6.16二百萬人的遊行，兩個月後帶同精心製作的反送中模型再次來到維園，是因為感到政府完全無視市民，即使已到了有少女右眼中槍和封機場等局面，也是完全沒有回應，所以他們認為必需要再次站出來，以及在街頭展示這套模型。及後下起大雨，他們一邊收拾模型，一邊說：「催淚彈也不怕，幾滴雨怕甚麼？」 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n法政匯思：警選擇性執法<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n輪椅生命鬥士：唔發聲玩完<br />\n<br />\n警西環屯重兵 見黑衣即查<br />\n醫護撐爆眼女 聲討高永文<br />\n年輕人製爆眼Minion轟警講大話<br />\n勇武派卸下裝備 做一日和理非<br />\n無懼金手指 國泰空姐上街<br />\n公開信：下跪不能絕處逢生<br />\n抗議港航打壓 50地勤請病假<br />\nDSE考生撐罷課：講緊香港將來<br />\n派191億 買不到港人良心<br />\n阮民安：港人似我打不死<br />\n錢志健促地產商發贖罪券<br />\n張達明：和理非要為青年豁出去<br />\n法政匯思：警選擇性執法<br />\n輪椅生命鬥士：唔發聲玩完<br />\n流水式集會 軒尼詩道順逆並行<br />\n巴黎黃背心聲援香港抗爭<br />\n親中學生暴力踩場 澳洲議員轟中共操控<br />\n警SMS提示非人人收到<br />\n水炮車黃竹坑戒備<br />\n內地網民夜貼小字報打氣<br />\n台「巴哈」網似連登 免翻牆暢所欲言<br />\n官媒譏示威者蟑螂 不提維園集會<br />\n葵芳人追究警放催淚彈<br />\n梁愛詩拒答駐軍殺人權限<br />\n促美制裁港府 白宮聯署達標<br />\n黃之鋒：市民爭取自決權利<br />\n張建宗陳茂波學舌抹黑抗爭<br />\n無懼京官林鄭文攻武嚇170萬和理非 堅持初心"},{"pid":"2849a60246b085f6460d34d30cdf8c73bfac6453","tid":1486983,"uid":276555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8db3a4e14dbd83b11d86ddc06c07a491f5bf74c9","tid":1486983,"uid":115715,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T05:28:29.000Z","msg":"3個月? 即係未開波就開始整?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:19:13.000Z","msg":"6 7 8月加埋差唔多3個月啦<br />\nbtw好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77bbc963bd4adec52f7650f788eb44ba43a77fa9","tid":1486983,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:35:32.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"6c7ade3459fdf54487da12555a4392681aae18c6","tid":1486983,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"想買返一set"},{"pid":"dc187e33fec56c5497d928703f0fa68bd88e01b0","tid":1486983,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T08:55:16.000Z","msg":"冇絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc914a8e153e95259ca96787de13b08b2f394c7e","tid":1486983,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"e6ee7dd7231e5f10b70c06c2cfad8ccf49cd85e4","tid":1486983,"uid":293667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:50:06.000Z","msg":"[文宣組注意 幫推]8.18後又是新開始 工作又要重新開始了 繼續撕一貼十精神<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487760</a>"}]}